text: Trongsa District is one of the 20 districts in Bhutan. The administrative centre is Trongsa Dzong. Wangchuck Centennial Park and Jigme Singye Wangchuck National Park are both in the district. There are five village blocks: *Dragteng Gewog *Korphu Gewog *Langthil Gewog *Nubi Gewog *Tangsibji Gewog Category:Districts of Bhutan
title: Trongsa District
